data.description: Here it is! Room to grow in this contemporary 4 Bedroom home with walk out lower level and 3 car garage! Wonderful and picturesque lot on a quiet cul-de-sac. Three full baths, with new toilets and a jetted tub (main level). Enjoy your  extensive wrap around deck and watch the birds with your morning coffee. Lovely patio with stone walkway and walls. Newer roof (2020) and carpets. Make this gem yours today.
